<p>
<h2>The Wall</h2>
<p>
The wall is a short but significant barrier running north/south across the
foothills of the north mountain. You can either go round the north end,
round the south end, or through a small gap (if you're carrying nothing) at
the <font color="#00ee00">narrow road between lands</font>. It's a mild
annoyance, nothing more, and is probably only there to force newbies to learn
to leave the road every so often :-) . Historically, it marks the eastern edge of
the original <i>MUD 1</i>, with everything beyond it added on since. To this
day, the stuff to the west of it is somehow more the &quot;core&quot; of
the game than anything that lies to its east.
<p>
